---
import GlasshouseLayout from '../../components/GlasshouseLayout.astro';
---

<GlasshouseLayout title="Case Files — LDI" activePage="/work/case-files">

  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="page-eyebrow">Case Files</div>
    <h1 class="page-headline">Internal deployments first.</h1>
    <p class="page-sub">We don't pitch client work we haven't run ourselves. These are LDI's live internal deployments — each one is a real system operating under real conditions. Client engagements come after the internal proof of concept holds up.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="case-grid">

    <article class="case-card case-card--featured">
      <div class="case-meta">
        <span class="case-status case-status--operational">Operational</span>
        <span class="case-id">FILE — 001</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="case-title">LDI Website</h2>
      <div class="case-track">Creative Systems · Content Engine</div>
      <p class="case-body">The site you're on. Astro 7 + Cloudflare Pages. Full design system with dark attraction aesthetic and light Glasshouse corporate identity running as two distinct modes under a single build. Deployed continuously via GitHub → Cloudflare. Sub-second TTFB globally.</p>
      <div class="case-outcomes">
        <div class="case-outcome">
          <span class="outcome-label">Architecture</span>
          <span class="outcome-val">Astro + Cloudflare Pages</span>
        </div>
        <div class="case-outcome">
          <span class="outcome-label">Status</span>
          <span class="outcome-val">Live — this session</span>
        </div>
        <div class="case-outcome">
          <span class="outcome-label">Key result</span>
          <span class="outcome-val">Two visual identities, one coherent build</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="case-card">
      <div class="case-meta">
        <span class="case-status case-status--operational">Operational</span>
        <span class="case-id">FILE — 002</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="case-title">Mission Intake Pipeline</h2>
      <div class="case-track">Automation Systems · Research OS</div>
      <p class="case-body">The intake wizard on this page feeds a structured JSON pipeline. 6-step guided brief replaces the vague discovery call. JSON output with copy/download. Webhook delivery to structured intake queue in active development.</p>
      <div class="case-outcomes">
        <div class="case-outcome">
          <span class="outcome-label">Architecture</span>
          <span class="outcome-val">Vanilla JS wizard + JSON pipeline</span>
        </div>
        <div class="case-outcome">
          <span class="outcome-label">Status</span>
          <span class="outcome-val">Form live — webhook in dev</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="case-card">
      <div class="case-meta">
        <span class="case-status case-status--operational">Operational</span>
        <span class="case-id">FILE — 003</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="case-title">Bob's Fortune Emporium</h2>
      <div class="case-track">Executive Assistant OS · Operator Dashboards</div>
      <p class="case-body">Autonomous agent system running the fortune oracle and ambient character layer of the Attraction. Bob is the orchestrator: multi-model routing, async handoff bus, cron-scheduled operations, and real-time response. Built on the BRAINLab agent platform (Hermes gateway).</p>
      <div class="case-outcomes">
        <div class="case-outcome">
          <span class="outcome-label">Architecture</span>
          <span class="outcome-val">Hermes gateway · Mac Mini orchestrator</span>
        </div>
        <div class="case-outcome">
          <span class="outcome-label">Status</span>
          <span class="outcome-val">Running — nightly cron + live dispatch</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="case-card">
      <div class="case-meta">
        <span class="case-status case-status--pilot">Pilot Ready</span>
        <span class="case-id">FILE — 004</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="case-title">Ghost's Workshop</h2>
      <div class="case-track">Creative Systems · Content Engine</div>
      <p class="case-body">Creative systems and content pipeline powering the Workshop district of the Attraction. AI-assisted generation with human curation and lore consistency enforcement. Acts as internal proof-of-concept for content engine client engagements.</p>
      <div class="case-outcomes">
        <div class="case-outcome">
          <span class="outcome-label">Architecture</span>
          <span class="outcome-val">Multi-agent creative pipeline</span>
        </div>
        <div class="case-outcome">
          <span class="outcome-label">Status</span>
          <span class="outcome-val">Pilot — not yet client-ready</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="case-card case-card--featured-2">
      <div class="case-meta">
        <span class="case-status case-status--dev">In Development</span>
        <span class="case-id">FILE — 005</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="case-title">Signal Engine / Research OS</h2>
      <div class="case-track">Research OS · Knowledge Systems</div>
      <p class="case-body">Multi-source research synthesis, monitoring, and structured brief generation. BRAINLab's internal Research OS — ongoing monitoring across sources, AI-assisted synthesis, and scheduled brief delivery. The first Research OS track we plan to offer to external clients. Internal version running on the BRAINLab platform with Perplexity + Claude routing.</p>
      <div class="case-outcomes">
        <div class="case-outcome">
          <span class="outcome-label">Architecture</span>
          <span class="outcome-val">Hermes · Perplexity · Claude · cron delivery</span>
        </div>
        <div class="case-outcome">
          <span class="outcome-label">Status</span>
          <span class="outcome-val">Internal — client release TBD</span>
        </div>
        <div class="case-outcome">
          <span class="outcome-label">Priority</span>
          <span class="outcome-val">First external track to ship</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

  </div>

  <div class="cta-strip">
    <div class="cta-strip-copy">
      <div class="cta-eyebrow">Ready to start?</div>
      <p>Every client engagement begins with a mission brief. It takes 10 minutes and replaces the vague discovery call.</p>
    </div>
    <a href="/work/intake" class="btn-cta">Start a Mission Brief →</a>
  </div>

</GlasshouseLayout>

<style>
  /* ── Page header ── */
  .page-header {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    max-width: 640px;
  }
  .page-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gh-brass);
    font-family: var(--gh-mono);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .page-headline {
    font-family: var(--gh-serif);
    font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 3.5vw, 2.75rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gh-text);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    line-height: 1.12;
    margin-bottom: 0.875rem;
  }
  .page-sub {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--gh-muted);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  /* ── Case grid ── */
  .case-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  .case-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.68);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border: 1px solid var(--gh-border);
    border-radius: var(--gh-radius);
    padding: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.875rem;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    transition: box-shadow 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }
  .case-card:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.10);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  .case-card--featured { border-color: rgba(201,157,76,0.25); }
  .case-card--featured-2 { grid-column: 1 / -1; }

  /* Meta row */
  .case-meta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }
  .case-status {
    font-size: 0.58rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-family: var(--gh-mono);
    padding: 0.22em 0.7em;
    border-radius: 100px;
  }
  .case-status--operational {
    background: rgba(76, 175, 110, 0.12);
    color: #2e7d4f;
  }
  .case-status--pilot {
    background: rgba(61, 127, 189, 0.12);
    color: #2a5f96;
  }
  .case-status--dev {
    background: rgba(201, 157, 76, 0.12);
    color: #8a6620;
  }
  .case-id {
    font-size: 0.58rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    color: var(--gh-faint);
    font-family: var(--gh-mono);
  }

  /* Card body */
  .case-title {
    font-family: var(--gh-serif);
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gh-text);
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .case-track {
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--gh-brass);
    font-family: var(--gh-mono);
  }
  .case-body {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--gh-muted);
    line-height: 1.65;
    flex: 1;
  }

  /* Outcomes */
  .case-outcomes {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding-top: 0.875rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--gh-border);
    margin-top: auto;
  }
  .case-outcome {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }
  .outcome-label {
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gh-faint);
    font-family: var(--gh-mono);
    min-width: 80px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .outcome-val {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--gh-muted);
  }

  /* ── CTA strip ── */
  .cta-strip {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border: 1px solid var(--gh-border);
    border-radius: var(--gh-radius);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 3rem;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }
  .cta-strip-copy {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    flex: 1;
  }
  .cta-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gh-brass);
    font-family: var(--gh-mono);
  }
  .cta-strip-copy p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--gh-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 50ch;
  }
  .btn-cta {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
    background: var(--gh-blue);
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 10px;
    white-space: nowrap;
    transition: background 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .btn-cta:hover {
    background: #3270aa;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(61,127,189,0.3);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .case-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .case-card--featured-2 { grid-column: 1; }
    .cta-strip { flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; align-items: flex-start; }
    .btn-cta { width: 100%; text-align: center; }
  }
</style>
